<div class="comment"><div class="commtext c00">&gt; <i>other epochs work too (e.g. Apollo_Time in Jai uses the Apollo 11 rocket landing at July 20, 1969 20:17:40 UTC).</i><p>I see someone else is a Vernor Vinge fan.<p>But it&#x27;s kind of a wild choice for an epoch, when you&#x27;re very likely to be interfacing with systems whose Epoch starts approximately five months later.</div><div class="reply"><p><font size="1"><u><a href="reply?id=44371005&amp;goto=item%3Fid%3D44370426%2344371005" rel="nofollow">reply</a></u></font></div></div></td></tr>
